data.description: Rare authentic custom Santa Fe ranch on 2.5 acres, with an FCP raised center-aisle barn built in 2020. Gated arched courtyard entry leads to grand rustic door. Gorgeous chiseled-edged stone flooring throughout, massive rough-hewn beams grace the ceilings, extensive art lighting, custom vintage built-in bar, multiple fireplaces, and a spectacular kitchen. Newer Jenn-Air appliances, 6-burner gas cooktop, pot filler, custom stainless steel hood, Miele coffee maker, dual ovens, granite countertops and backsplash, island bar seating and striking high-gloss lighted cabinetry accented with artistic designer wallpaper. The primary bedroom includes a bonus room with built-in cabinets, 2 large walk-ins and an exceptional spa bath with steam shower. Barn features 3 12x12 stalls, 12x16 foaling stall, tack room and 12 x 12 wash/groom area with heated water when needed. Pavers in both the center aisle and under the extended porch. Three stalls have attached runs of approximately 25'. Horses will beat the heat with the large center aisle fans, and which are also installed over three of the individual stalls, as well. This equestrian oasis also boasts a beautiful 200' x 120' lighted arena which will be a welcome relief on warm summer nights.
